    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been well-maintained, perfect for someone who wants a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. It drives like a dream and is super comfy for those long road trips or just zipping around town. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
