    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking reliability and style. The exterior finish maintains a high-gloss luster, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical signs of careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather seats show light bolstering wear but remain soft and free of tears. Every electronic component, from the heated seats to the navigation system, is fully operational. Mechanically, the car is sound, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a brake pad replacement. It sits on a set of premium tires with significant tread life remaining, ensuring it is ready for the road immediately upon purchase.",
