    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hi there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend getaways. I've taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner right away! If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that\u2019s been well-loved, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
