    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, the drivetrain remains tight with a factory limited-slip differential ensuring optimal torque distribution. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis' known harmonic stress points. Riding on refreshed bushings and a balanced MacPherson strut/multi-link suspension setup, this driver-focused machine offers the tactile feedback and analog precision sought by purists. The rod bearings have been serviced, and the cooling system has been upgraded with an aluminum radiator for improved thermal efficiency during spirited driving.",
